title: Veggie Dumplings & Veggie Spring Rolls Board with Gyoza Sauce, Pickled Cucumbers & Sesame Slaw | 4 Servings
description: SUMM! is committed to making their products in small batches using high-quality ingredients and a whole lot of love! This easy-to-assemble board comes with SUMM!’s dippable gyoza (Japanese-style dumplings)—stuffed with a blend of cabbage, carrot, and corn—plus their crispy veggie spring rolls. Turn this spread into an obsession-worthy meatless appetizer by whipping up crunchy sesame slaw and tangy pickled cucumbers to serve on the side.

